### Listar todos os pagamentos
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter pagamento por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter pagamentos do usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/user/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar pagamento PIX
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ticketId": "1",
  "method": "PIX",
  "amount": 150.00
}

### Criar pagamento Cartão de Crédito
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ticketId": "1",
  "method": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "installments": 3
}

### Aprovar pagamento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Rejeitar pagamento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Estornar pagamento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payments/1/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter estatísticas de pagamentos
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
